					Full Description



		Hearts United Group Co., Ltd. is a Japan-based holding company. Through its wholly owned subsidiary, the Company is principally engaged in the operation of debugging business, media business and others. The Company’s debugging operation provides services to detect and report the bugs of software through the operation test, and the testing targets comprise home video game software, online games and arcade games; mobile contents, Websites for mobile devices and mobile terminal bodies, as well as gaming machines. The media operation is engaged in the operation of gaming site 4Gamer.net, which publishes gaming-related information to general consumers, and also provides advertising services. The others business provides development outsourcing services to support the whole development processes of game software. It also operates a portal site named Fuguai.com, which provides film production services and bug information, and provides various development support services, among others.
» Full Overview of 3676.T







