In The News:




 


                                                    Eiichi Miyazawa is no longer serving in their position at Hearts United Group Co., Ltd.                                                





                                     July 3, 2017  •  RelSci                                








Hearts United Group Co., Ltd. »
Hearts United Group Co., Ltd. is a holding company that engages in the management of its subsidiaries. It operates through the following segments: Debugging, Media, Creative, and Others. The Debugging segment offers user debugging and other related services in the areas of amusement, consumer games, and digital solutions. The Media segment manages game information site 4Gamer.net and offers promotional activities support services. The Creative segment covers the 3 dimension computer graphics (3DCG) content development, development outsourcing, video production, and support services in the creative area for general content production. The Others segment deals with systems development and Fugai.com business. The company was founded on October 1, 2013 and is headquartered in Tokyo, Japan.




In The News:




                            Eiichi Miyazawa is no longer serving in their position at Hearts United Group Co., Ltd.                            


                            July 3, 2017  •  RelSci                        





                            Takeshi Matsumoto is no longer serving in their board position at Hearts United Group Co., Ltd.                            


                            July 3, 2017  •  RelSci                        









Hearts United Group Co., Ltd. »
Hearts United Group Co., Ltd. is a holding company that engages in the management of its subsidiaries. It operates through the following segments: Debugging, Media, Creative, and Others. The Debugging segment offers user debugging and other related services in the areas of amusement, consumer games, and digital solutions. The Media segment manages game information site 4Gamer.net and offers promotional activities support services. The Creative segment covers the 3 dimension computer graphics (3DCG) content development, development outsourcing, video production, and support services in the creative area for general content production. The Others segment deals with systems development and Fugai.com business. The company was founded on October 1, 2013 and is headquartered in Tokyo, Japan.






